&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Come join Karat&#39;s &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://karat.com/candidates/interview-engineers/&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Community!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Karat is seeking talented U.S.-based engineers ready to commit to a dedicated, availability-based contract through Q3 2026.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking U.S.-based contractors to join our Interview Engineer community with consistent, dedicated availability of 40 hours per week through Q3 2026&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a fixed-term, four-month engagement with a structured weekly availability commitment through Q3 2026. You will hold a consistent block of hours each week during which you are available to conduct interviews, including short-notice requests. Availability outside of standard business hours and on weekends is welcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a strong fit if you are between full-time positions, on a planned leave from your current role, or looking for consistent, meaningful contract work over a defined period.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commit to a consistent weekly availability block of 40 hours to accept and conduct interview asstructuredsignments, including short-notice requests; evenings and weekends are welcome.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct structured 60-minute technical interviews through Karat&#39;s platform across domains such as back-end, full-stack, front-end, and system design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submit thorough written evaluations of each candidate&#39;s coding approach, technical knowledge, and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain Karat&#39;s standards for structured, inclusive, bias-mitigated interviewing throughout your engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This contract will be a good fit if you have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of professional software engineering experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience conducting technical interviews, either through a formal employer program or independently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written and verbal English communication skills; clear, efficient evaluation write-ups matter here&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A reliable home setup: stable internet connection, working webcam, and microphone&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Genuine availability to hold a consistent weekly block for the full three-month term; this is not a pick-up-when-you-want arrangement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Engagement details:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 4 months&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Weekly commitment:&lt;/strong&gt; 40 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Availability windows:&lt;/strong&gt; Flexible, including evenings and weekends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation:&lt;/strong&gt; Hourly rate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Remote; must be currently located in the United States&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Classification: &lt;/strong&gt;Independent Contractor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Upon contract conclusion, contractors may opt into Karat&#39;s standard Interview Engineer program, which operates on a per-interview compensation model.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
